Class UserService

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.moodroid.service.UserService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UserInterface

    @Singleton
public class UserService
extends java.lang.Object
implements UserInterface
    This class implements user operations such as handling username functions as well as dealing with follow requests from other users, and sending your own follow request.
